pn.extension()
gv.extension('bokeh')

zarr_file = 'https://data.rda.ucar.edu/pythia_era5_24/annual_means/temp_2m_annual_1940_2023.zarr'

era5_ds = xr.open_dataset(zarr_file, engine= 'zarr')

var_select = pn.widgets.Select(
    name = 'Variable',
    options = ['VAR_2T']
)
var_select

era5_var_ds = era5_ds[var_select.value]

# Select the year via a slider based on the min and max times in the Dataset

year_slider = pn.widgets.IntSlider(
    name = 'Year',
    start = era5_var_ds.time.dt.year.values.min(),
    end = era5_var_ds.time.dt.year.values.max(),
)

# Color map selection, based off popular maps listed in matplotlib.colormaps()

cmap_select = pn.widgets.Select(
    name = 'Colormap',
    options = ['viridis', 'inferno', 'inferno_r', 'kb', 'coolwarm', 'coolwarm_r', 'Blues', 'Blues_r']
)

datetime.datetime(year_slider.value, 1, 1)

datetime.datetime(1940, 1, 1, 0, 0)

def plot_ds(da, year, cmap):
    year_slider.start = da.time.dt.year.values.min()
    year_slider.end = da.time.dt.year.values.max()
    
    if 'long_name' in da.attrs:
        var_long_name = da.attrs['long_name']
    else:
        var_long_name = var
    
    if 'units' in da.attrs:
        clabel = f'{var_long_name} ({da.attrs["units"]})'
    else:
        clabel = f'{var_long_name} (undefined units)'
    
    return rasterize(
        da.sel(time=datetime.datetime(year, 1, 1), method='nearest').hvplot(
            x='longitude',
            y='latitude',
            geo=True,
            coastline=True,
            cmap=cmap,
            clabel=clabel
        ).opts(
            title=f"{var_long_name} anomaly on {year_slider.value}",
            frame_width=400
        ))

pn.Row(
    pn.Column(
        var_select,
        year_slider,
        cmap_select,
    ),
    pn.panel(
        pn.bind(
            plot_ds, 
            da=era5_var_ds,
            year=year_slider,
            cmap=cmap_select
        )
    )
).servable()
